    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/693ed41118225b055397b6ea7684cabb.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/693ed41118225b055397b6ea7684cabb.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/693ed41118225b055397b6ea7684cabb.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>在《巨人之肩》中，您将同时控制一台挥舞着剑的机器人和一只能开枪的太空青蛙。这是一款色彩绚丽、充满爆炸性的科幻迷宫游戏，旨在考验您的团队合作能力。<br><br>熵的力量正在星际间蔓延混乱，腐化生命行星，催促宇宙的热寂。在通灵猫头鹰的带领下，一支富有斗志的太空幸存者团队正在努力恢复平衡。神秘的机甲！精准射击的两栖动物！他们必须共同穿越敌人的攻势，将光明和生机带回银河！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >最佳朋友模式</h2><br>独自前行很危险！可以单人游玩，或者与朋友组队，每人分别控制青蛙或机器人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/e52a783135593ce9372087febbf4f3f6.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/e52a783135593ce9372087febbf4f3f6.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/e52a783135593ce9372087febbf4f3f6.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四人军团</h2><br>在四人在线合作中与熵之力作战。你们的团队合作是否足够强大以求生存<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/a70f1274a830d0915f92455a8dca5cf2.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/a70f1274a830d0915f92455a8dca5cf2.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/a70f1274a830d0915f92455a8dca5cf2.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >边走边成长</h2><br>体验短暂的类地下城冒险快乐，随着探索、成长，在永不停止的随机关卡之旅中逐渐变得强大无比。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/dd41a9bfde4dd3613caceede86b15c6a.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/dd41a9bfde4dd3613caceede86b15c6a.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/dd41a9bfde4dd3613caceede86b15c6a.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遥远的星系</h2><br>在爆炸性的多彩星球上射击和劈斩，与此同时在战斗中恢复生命和光明，将破碎的世界修复。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/d670675610df0f58d84ccdfd0a0f4845.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/d670675610df0f58d84ccdfd0a0f4845.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/d670675610df0f58d84ccdfd0a0f4845.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有价值的战利品</h2><br>从抓钩到发光手榴弹，每个新的道具都可以彻底改变你的力量和玩法风格。混搭不同的能力，创造出属于自己的招式组合！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/01810184bd3ac1ac0f13f33d37c8800a.poster.avif?t=1750704755\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/01810184bd3ac1ac0f13f33d37c8800a.webm?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283880/extras/01810184bd3ac1ac0f13f33d37c8800a.mp4?t=1750704755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
